Second Department,

September, 1961.

(September 7, 1961) In the Matter of Maria Bricker, as Committee for Anna Krimer, an Incompetent Person, Appellant. William Krimer, Respondent.

The record and appellant’s brief must be served and filed on or before October 9, 1961. Nolan, P. J., Beldock, Ughetta, Kleinfeld and Christ, JJ., concur.
